{"tid":714963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］蔡少芬5歲細女幼稚園畢業","createTime":"2018-06-24T05:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T18:29:28.000Z","uid":48905,"like":93,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"87d518f1b17073ab668dcfe40348c13512bb2961","tid":714963,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"44歲蔡少芬（Ada）同老公張晉話咁快結婚十年，步入錫婚，大女楚兒（湯圓）現年7歲，細女信兒（包子）亦已經5歲。<br />\n<br />\n昨日係包子嘅幼稚園畢業，張晉喺社交網貼相並留言：「今天是信兒（包子）在幼兒園的最後一天，一眨眼就兩年了，還真有點兒捨不得。不過暑假後就能和姐姐背着小書包，手牽手一起上學放學啦，內心也挺期待的。」<br />\n<br />\n相中Ada同老公齊齊陪包子返學，着天鵝公主裙嘅包子十分可愛，Ada轉貼老公帖文並寫道：「今天也是父親節的活動！真好！最後一天兩個意義！不捨但期待！」由於幼稚園有好多主題活動，之前Ada經常要D.I.Y.為囡囡炮製唔同造型，不過包子今次嘅公主look太漂亮，陳法蓉抵死留言：「張家可愛機靈的小包子一天一天長大了，今天這件美麗的天鵝服：目測不是涼涼（Ada）親手做的，為何？因為裙子很美。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/132553_f7a15dea219da3be2c07b5a6575ce8d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F132553_f7a15dea219da3be2c07b5a6575ce8d0.jpg&h=e6b4d7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif&h=74a0e790&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d182af3acc43bd278de13edc8c7847482b88900b","tid":714963,"uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔快啲去傾定婚約"},{"pid":"338d681447640b39553a5954b55c18642e48ab02","tid":714963,"uid":42820,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"幾靚女窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc79a07ed69755964abd39da2dbb86cf3824695","tid":714963,"uid":3180,"like":143,"dislike":4,"score":139,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"大女同蔡少芬餅印咁<img 